Class Knight

  • java.lang.Object
    • knightsEnd.players.Knight
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Blunt, Swords
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlackKnight, WhiteKnight

    public class Knight
extends java.lang.Object
implements Swords, Blunt
    The Class Knight. This class implements interfaces Swords and Blunt. This class also holds all of the information on a Knight.
